Package explicit.modelviews

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DTMCAlteredDistributions
    A view of a DTMC where for selected states the transitions are changed.
    DTMCView
    Base class for a DTMC view, i.e., a virtual DTMC that is obtained by mapping from some other model on-the-fly.
    EquivalenceRelationInteger
    An object representing an equivalence relation between integers (typically state indices), from a given list of equivalent classes (each represented by a BitSet).
    EquivalenceRelationInteger.KeepSingletons  
    MDPAdditionalChoices
    An MDPView that takes an existing MDP and adds additional choices to certain states.
    MDPDroppedAllChoices
    An MDPView that takes an existing MDP and removes all outgoing choices for certain states.
    MDPDroppedChoicesCached
    An MDPView that takes an existing MDP and removes certain choices.
    MDPEquiv
    An MDPView that provides a quotient view on the original MDP, given an equivalence relation.
    MDPFromDTMC
    An MDPView that takes an existing DTMC and pretends it is actually an MDP, i.e., in every state there is a single choice.
    MDPView
    Base class for an MDP view, i.e., a virtual MDP that is obtained by mapping from some other model on-the-fly.
    ModelView
    Base class for an DTMCView or MDPView, handling common tasks.
